text: Emma Regan (born January 28, 2000) is a Canadian international soccer player who plays as a defender. She appeared for the Canada women's national soccer team in one match at the 2018 CONCACAF Women's Championship. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian women's soccer players Category:Canada women's international soccer players Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Texas Longhorns women's soccer players
